cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.CY

This paper belongs to the field of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with the task of humor recognition and generation. Additionally, it involves the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.AI) for humor scoring. The dataset creation and annotation process also involves crowd-sourcing techniques (cs.LG) and statistical analysis (cs.SD). Finally, the paper touches upon the subjective nature of humor, which can be studied in the field of Cybernetics (cs.CY).
